## Dimension: Faithfulness (HARD CONSTRAINT)

**Definition**: The degree to which the synthesis accurately represents source material without introducing novel claims, interpretations, or distortions.

**Why This Matters**: The synthesis serves as controlled feedback in a Delphi process. Any novel claims or misattributions undermine trust and compromise the scientific integrity of the advice artefact.

